methods.getFormatBaseColumn:
Returns the base column-name used to create a formatting column via getFormatExpression(String) method

:param selectColumn: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.select.SelectColumn) - a SelectColumn returned from the getFormatExpression(String) method
:return: (java.lang.String) the baseColumn used to define the provided selectColumn

text: A factory to create SelectColumns from an input expression.
